description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;An opportunity has arisen at Mid Yorkshire Hospitals NHS Trust to appoint on a permanent basis as a part-time Medical Secretary. This would be a 30 hour post with the working pattern being Monday, Wednesday, Thursday and Friday 9.00am to 5.00 pm.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The successful candidate will work as part of the Cardiology Department within Mid Yorkshire Hospitals NHS Trust. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The post holder will work primarily from the Pinderfields site, however will be required to provide cover at Dewsbury Hospital as and when required and will be responsible for providing secretarial and administrative support to the Cardiology team. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;We would welcome applications from self-motivated and flexible individuals with excellent organisational and prioritisation skills. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;You will need to have RSA3 typing qualification or equivalent.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The successful candidate should be equipped with good interpersonal and communication skills, combined with a committed and flexible approach to work.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;For further information or an informal chat please contact:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Donna Maddox-Cliff&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Medical Secretary Team Leader – Cardiology &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;01924 542217&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
